cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with pedestrian detection in images. It may also belong to Robotics (cs.RO) as pedestrian detection is an important task for autonomous robots. Additionally, the use of synthetic human-agents for training may fall under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Finally, the concept of Spawn Probability Map may be related to Graphics (cs.GR).
